ShareOverview

Levy, Harkins & Co. is in the business of buying and selling securities such as stocks, bonds, mutual funds and other investment-related products. This broker is registered with the SEC (#24181) and can engage in securities transactions on behalf of its customers (as a broker) or for its own account (as a dealer). Registered with 11 U.S. states and territories
Firm data current as of 12/31/2015




